---

Third-party data and assets used by this project, with their own licences:

- **Boreas dataset** (UTIAS-ASRL): Burnett et al., *Boreas: A Multi-Season
  Autonomous Driving Dataset*, IJRR 2023. CC BY 4.0 — required attribution
  applied in `src/video_runtime/fetch_track.py` track registry.
- **Mapillary imagery**: Mapillary v4 API, used under the open-data licence at
  https://www.mapillary.com/dataset.
- **DISK** (Tyszkiewicz et al., NeurIPS 2020): pretrained weights via
  `kornia.feature.DISK`, MIT licence.
- **LightGlue** (Lindenberger et al., ICCV 2023): pretrained weights via
  `kornia.feature.LightGlue`, Apache-2.0 licence.
- **Mask2Former** (Cheng et al., CVPR 2022): pretrained weights via
  `transformers` (`facebook/mask2former-swin-tiny-cityscapes-semantic`),
  Apache-2.0 licence.
- **EB Garamond, Inter, JetBrains Mono fonts** (in `assets/fonts/`): SIL Open
  Font Licence 1.1.

All learned components are used frozen — no training, no fine-tuning, and
no snowy frames touch any model weights or annotation pipeline.
